title: PP-90, Bhakkar: PTI candidate Irfanullah Niazi clinches victory
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jul 17 (APP):Irfanullah Khan Niazi, a candidate of PTI clinched Punjab Assemblyâ€™s PP-90 Bukkur seat by securing 77,865 votes.
According to the results,Saeed Akbar Khan of PML-N got 66,513 votes.
Muhammad Amjad Jamil of TLP secured 3,270 votes.The turn out remained 66.86 percent.
